      { q: "Which of these best describes your current role in the spread of God's Word?", options: ["Receiver only — I consume but don't share", "Occasional sharer when convenient", "Active distributor in my circle", "A committed herald — giving, going, and publishing"], answer: 3, insight: "Every level matters, and every step forward counts. Read today's devotional to discover how God sees your role in the Gospel." }
